So how do you plan to present it?

00:41:05.940 --> 00:41:06.660
Actually,

00:41:07.300 --> 00:41:09.180
we want to make

00:41:09.580 --> 00:41:11.540
the high-cultural image of wine

00:41:11.980 --> 00:41:12.340
more accessible.

