They want to film a documentary

00:41:18.980 --> 00:41:20.340
about ballet at our school,

00:41:21.060 --> 00:41:23.220
hoping to let more people
understand ballet.

00:41:24.300 --> 00:41:25.180
That's a good thing.

00:41:25.380 --> 00:41:25.820
Madam,

00:41:26.460 --> 00:41:27.580
what do you need me to do?

00:41:28.140 --> 00:41:30.340
They want me to recommend a teacher

00:41:30.580 --> 00:41:33.300
to participate in the filming
of their documentary.

00:41:33.700 --> 00:41:35.620
I'd like to recommend you.

00:41:37.900 --> 00:41:38.900
Ballet

00:41:39.460 --> 00:41:40.860
has always been seen

00:41:40.860 --> 00:41:43.460
as a very painful art form.

