This is also the reason

00:42:06.420 --> 00:42:08.980
you have never given up
on ballet all these years.

00:42:09.580 --> 00:42:10.060
Right?

00:42:12.500 --> 00:42:15.660
Changing the public's
fixed perception of ballet

00:42:16.180 --> 00:42:17.980
and letting more people
fall in love with it

00:42:18.260 --> 00:42:21.020
were my original intentions
for founding this school.

00:42:22.260 --> 00:42:22.820
Ting,

00:42:24.260 --> 00:42:25.100
I know

00:42:25.460 --> 00:42:27.820
