in the public eye after retiring.

00:42:28.540 --> 00:42:29.260
It's okay.

00:42:29.740 --> 00:42:30.580
I understand.

00:42:30.820 --> 00:42:33.180
If you don't want to participate,
just tell me.

00:42:33.660 --> 00:42:34.020
Madam,

00:42:34.180 --> 00:42:34.860
I'll do it.

00:42:36.140 --> 00:42:36.780
Indeed.

00:42:37.420 --> 00:42:39.100
If we want more people to understand

00:42:39.980 --> 00:42:40.860
and recognize ballet,

00:42:41.380 --> 00:42:43.820
we need the power of media platforms.

00:42:44.540 --> 00:42:46.540
Just tell me what you need me to do.

00:42:48.180 --> 00:42:48.980
Great.

00:42:49.820 --> 00:42:51.300
Thank you, Ting.

